metadata.name: Magical Circus
metadata.description:
When the red stage curtain opens, there is a mysterious world that I have never seen
It is gorgeously beautiful and captivates the viewer.
With mysterious music played
Now, the beginning of magical circus, the beginning

赤い緞帳が開くと、今まで見たことのない不思議な世界
煌びやかにに美しく、見る人を魅了します。
不思議な音楽を奏でて
さあ、魔法のサーカスのはじまり、はじまりー
